      "repair_reason": "This is a draft feature with a concrete P2 setup bug, missing current-head real behavior proof, and a security/product decision around TLS interception, so it is not a safe automated repair lane yet.; Needs attention: The diff introduces child-scoped TLS interception and persisted proxy CA material, so it needs explicit maintainer/security review before merge.; Review finding: [P2] Register the interactive backend i... (sha=319362e6df4fdf647f6d5c4ce74413d9063296be)",
